org.eclipse.scada.vi.model.impl

Class GridChildImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • EObjectImpl
      • org.eclipse.scada.vi.model.impl.ChildImpl
        • org.eclipse.scada.vi.model.impl.GridChildImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Child, GridChild

    public class GridChildImpl
extends ChildImpl
implements GridChild
    An implementation of the model object 'Grid Child'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Horizontal Alignment
    • Vertical Alignment
    • Grab Horizontal Space
    • Grab Vertical Space
    • Span Cols
    • Span Rows
    • Width Hint
    • Height Hint
